text: Interstate 110 is the name of five Interstate Highways in the United States: *Interstate 110 (California), a north-south freeway running through Los Angeles, California *Interstate 110 (Florida), a spur route in Pensacola, Florida *Interstate 110 (Louisiana), a spur route in Baton Rouge, Louisiana *Interstate 110 (Mississippi), a spur route in Biloxi, Mississippi *Interstate 110 (Texas), a spur route in El Paso, Texas Category:Interstate Highways
title: Interstate 110
